Khi đó $\log_{2}3=\log_{2}7\cdot \log_{7}3=\dfrac{1}{xy-x}\cdot3x-2y=\dfrac{3-2y}{y-1}.$$\\$
Suy ra $\log_{3}2=\dfrac{y-1}{3-2y}$.$\\$
