\begin{align*}
\log_{54}168&=\dfrac{3}{1+3\frac{3-2y}{y-1}}+\dfrac{1}{xy-x+3(3x-2xy)}+\dfrac{1}{3+\frac{y-1}{3-2y}}\\
&=\dfrac{3(y-1)}{y-1+9-6y}+\dfrac{1}{8x-5xy}=\dfrac{3-2y}{8-5y}\\
&=\dfrac{3(y-1)}{8-5y}+\dfrac{3-2y}{8-5y}+\dfrac{1}{x(8-5y)}=\dfrac{xy+1}{8x-5xy}.
\end{align*}
Suy ra $a=1,\,b=-5,\,c=8$. Khi đó S=a+2b+3c=15.

Ta có $\log_{x^2+y^2}(2x+3y)\ge 1\Leftrightarrow (x-1)^2+\left(y-\dfrac{3}{2}\right)^2\le \dfrac{13}{4}$. Khi đó
\begin{eqnarray*}
P & = & 2x+y=2(x+1)+\left(y-\dfrac{3}{2}\right)+\dfrac{7}{2}\\
& \le & \sqrt{\left(2^2+1^2\right)\left[(x-1)^2+\left(y-\dfrac{3}{2}\right)^2\right]}+\dfrac{7}{2}\le \dfrac{7+\sqrt{65}}{2}.
\end{eqnarray*}
Do đó $P_{\max}=\dfrac{7+\sqrt{65}}{2}$ khi $\begin{cases} x-2y=-2\\ 2x+y=\dfrac{7+\sqrt{65}}{2}\end{cases}\Leftrightarrow \begin{cases} x=\dfrac{5+\sqrt{65}}{5}\\ y=\dfrac{15+\sqrt{65}}{10}\end{cases}$ (thỏa mãn $x^2+y^2>1$).
